        "solution_text": "$\\text{LCD of } 4, 6 = 12$\n$\\frac{3}{4} = \\frac{9}{12}$\n$\\frac{5}{6} = \\frac{10}{12}$\n$\\frac{3}{4} < \\frac{5}{6}$"
      },
      {
